config VPNHIDE
	bool "Hide VPN interfaces from selected Android UIDs"
	depends on PROC_FS
	default n
	help
	  Exports vpnhide_is_target_uid() and vpnhide_is_vpn_ifname() which
	  are called directly from net/core, net/ipv4, and net/ipv6 to filter
	  VPN interfaces out of ioctl/netlink/proc responses for processes
	  whose UID is written to /proc/vpnhide_targets.
